Probable errors¶

ImportError: /lib64/libstdc++.so.6¶

  • reason: the Gcc dynamic library version is too old.
  • how to solve:: #edit bash LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/home/feng/anaconda3/lib:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH export LD_LIBRARY_PATH
